data.description: Motivated Sellers.  All reasonable offers will be considered.  "Welcome to your dream home in Spring Valley Lake! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence with an office offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Nestled in the heart of a vibrant lake community, this commuter-friendly gem boasts an array of must-have features.  Step inside to discover a completely remodeled interior that exudes down-home elegance. The floor plan offers formal spaces, the combined living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it the ideal space for both gatherings and entertainment. Maintain interior comfort and piece of mind with new ducting and plumbing from the house to the street, ceiling fans and recessed lighting.   But the real showstopper awaits outside – an inviting inground vinyl pool that's perfect for those hot summer days (30 year warranty 04/2023 completed). The expansive backyard features plenty of concrete, making it low-maintenance and perfect for hosting outdoor BBQs or simply enjoying your own private oasis.  Imagine waking up to breathtaking views of the lake from the upstairs second main bedroom every morning. This property offers just that – a stunning lake view that will make every day feel like a vacation.  For the eco-conscious buyer, this home comes with solar and a new 200 amp panel, offering both energy efficiency and cost savings with a newly updated heating unit, circuit board and new thermostat. And, when it comes to safety, you'll have peace of mind with a Ring doorbell and cameras along with a smart lock on the front entry door, and 24-hour public safety patrol within the community.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. With its ideal location, luxurious pool, lake views, and recent renovations, it's a true gem. Schedule a showing today and experience the lifestyle you've always dreamed of in Spring Valley Lake!"
